    description:"These selectors target elements based on their relationship with other elements or by combining multiple selectors.",
    inputCode:"<style>\r\n  \/* Descendant selector: targets all <p> inside <div> *\/\r\n  div p {\r\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  \/* Child selector: targets only direct <p> children of <div> *\/\r\n  div > p {\r\n    font-weight: bold;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  \/* Adjacent sibling selector: targets the <p> immediately after an <h2> *\/\r\n  h2 + p {\r\n    font-style: italic;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  \/* General sibling selector: targets all <p> elements that come after an <h2> *\/\r\n  h2 ~ p {\r\n    color: gray;\r\n  }\r\n<\/style>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n  <p>This is a direct child paragraph inside div (bold + margin).<\/p>\r\n  <section>\r\n    <p>This is a nested paragraph inside a section inside div (margin only).<\/p>\r\n  <\/section>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Section Heading<\/h2>\r\n<p>This is immediately after h2 (italic + gray).<\/p>\r\n<p>This is also after h2 (gray only).<\/p>",
    outputCode:"<style>\r\n  .play div p {\r\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .play div > p {\r\n    font-weight: bold;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .play h2 + p {\r\n    font-style: italic;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .play h2 ~ p {\r\n    color: gray;\r\n  }\r\n<\/style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"play\">\r\n  <div>\r\n    <p>This is a direct child paragraph inside div (bold + margin).<\/p>\r\n    <section>\r\n      <p>\r\n        This is a nested paragraph inside a section inside div (margin only).\r\n      <\/p>\r\n    <\/section>\r\n  <\/div>\r\n\r\n  <h2>Section Heading<\/h2>\r\n  <p>This is immediately after h2 (italic + gray).<\/p>\r\n  <p>This is also after h2 (gray only).<\/p>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n  <p>This is outside the .play section (default style).<\/p>\r\n<\/div>",
