    inputCode:"<style>\r\n  .container {\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    width: 500px;\r\n    height: 300px;\r\n    margin: 50px auto;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  \/* Background element *\/\r\n  .background {\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    height: 100%;\r\n    background-color: #3498db;\r\n    z-index: 5;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  \/* Overlay element *\/\r\n  .overlay {\r\n    position: absolute; \/* Absolutely positioned relative to the container *\/\r\n    top: 50px;\r\n    left: 50px;\r\n    width: 400px;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); \/* Transparent dark overlay *\/\r\n    z-index: 10; \/* Higher z-index places this above the background *\/\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .text {\r\n    color: white;\r\n    font-size: 20px;\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n    line-height: 200px; \/* Vertically center the text *\/\r\n  }\r\n<\/style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"background\"><\/div>\r\n  <div class=\"overlay\">\r\n    <div class=\"text\">Overlay Content<\/div>\r\n  <\/div>\r\n<\/div>",
